  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a Pipewire</title>

    <para>
      The <application>pipewire</application> package contains a server and
userspace API to handle multimedia pipelines. This includes a universal API
to connect to multimedia devices, as well as sharing multimedia files
between applications.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

